commits.message: Sports cars can smash mosquitoes.  Fixes #881

New Ally Gates that can be created by leaders and only allow allies to pass through.  They are also spring-loaded, so allies can pass through without clicking (though they can also be opened and closed manually to let non-allies pass through).  Ownership of the gate is inherited along with leadership when the leader dies.  Part of jasonrohrer/OneLife#682
Can make burritos and tacos on the table.  Fixes #884
